### CLAUDE.md Update Mechanism

Added to root CLAUDE.md under "Folder-specific CLAUDE.md files" section:

**When to update:**
- Adding a new file → Add to inventory table
- Removing a file → Remove from inventory table
- Changing patterns → Update pattern section
- New anti-patterns → Add to anti-patterns list
- Breaking changes → Document in non-negotiables

**Maintenance triggers:**
- New hook → update `src/hooks/CLAUDE.md`
- New store → update `src/stores/CLAUDE.md`
- New widget → update `src/widgets/CLAUDE.md`
- New service → update `src/services/CLAUDE.md`
- New page → update `src/pages/CLAUDE.md`
- New component → update `src/components/CLAUDE.md`
- New E2E pattern → update `tests/CLAUDE.md`

### How to Run E2E Tests
```bash
npx playwright test                    # All tests
npx playwright test --ui               # Interactive UI
npx playwright test --project=chromium # Specific browser
npx playwright show-report             # View HTML report
```

